text:
Then...
I'll send it back without any further revisions.

Thank you.
It couldn't be better.

Who would have thought that what we
discussed would take shape like this──...

Well... I'm happy you're so pleased.
It makes me happy too.

Hehe...
I'm sure everyone had the same reaction, right?

Yeah, it seems like everyone liked it.
It's a relief.

It's the result of your hard work. I'm looking forward
to the day we all wear this outfit together.

Me too...!
Let me make some adjustments.

Got it.
I'll eagerly await with anticipation.

Hehe, I wonder what expressions everyone will
have when they put on this outfit...!
